{"EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:0002": {"attributes": "", "contents": [{"text": "What's wrong?"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:0003": {"attributes": "", "contents": [{"text": "Wait!"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:0004": {"attributes": "", "contents": [{"text": "I'll stop it!"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:0005": {"attributes": "", "contents": [{"text": "Ceremonial trident?"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:0006": {"attributes": "", "contents": [{"text": "Good-bye."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:0010": {"attributes": "", "contents": [{"text": "Ruta?"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:0011": {"attributes": "", "contents": [{"text": "Trident?"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:near00": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"text": "*grumble*"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:near01": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"text": "Hmph..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk00": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [4, 20]}}, {"text": "Hmm... "}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": "That "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "trident"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk01": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 125}}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [2, 14]}}, {"text": "HUH?!"}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "longer"}}, {"text": " A Hylian!"}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 100}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk02": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [8, 20]}}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 125}}, {"text": "And not just any Hylian!\nIsn't that you, Link?!"}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 100}}, {"text": "\n\nHow dare you show your face here!"}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "longer"}}, {"text": "\nAfter what you did"}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": " to Lady Mipha!"}, {"control": {"kind": "single_choice", "label": 3}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk04": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 125}}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [8, 14]}}, {"text": "What did you say?!"}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 100}}, {"text": "\n\n\nI, Trello,"}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": " shall punish you on behalf of\nour beloved Lady Mipha!\n\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [2, 12]}}, {"text": "*ahem* That's what I'd like to do,\nanyhow.\n\nBut I'm afraid those of us in the Zora\ncouncil have our hands full trying to\nfigure out what to do next about "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "Ruta"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "."}, {"control": {"kind": "raw", "one": {"eight": {"unknown_1": [[255, 255, 0, 0], [255, 255, 0, 0]], "field_1": [10, 0, 6], "field_2": [0, 0, 0, 3]}}}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk05": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 125}}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [8, 14]}}, {"text": "How can you be so shameless?!"}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 100}}, {"text": "\n\n\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [2, 1]}}, {"text": "The nerve!"}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "longer"}}, {"text": " I can assure you that we do\nnot now, nor have we ever, needed help\nfrom the likes of you!\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [2, 32]}}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 80}}, {"text": "*couuuugh*"}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 100}}, {"text": "\n\n\nI do not want to see your face around\nhere again!"}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "longer"}}, {"text": " Go on, get lost!"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk09": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [2, 14]}}, {"text": "Hmph..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk10": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [2, 14]}}, {"text": "Hmph... "}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": "Unbearable Hylian brat..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk11": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [2, 12]}}, {"text": "...\n\n\nUh-oh...\n\n\nThanks to your meddling,"}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": " you've gone\nand made me forget about the "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "trident\nI dropped"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": ".\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [11, 16]}}, {"text": "That's that, I guess...\nBut what do I do now?"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk12": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [2, 1]}}, {"text": "That is not your business!"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk13": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 11]}}, {"text": "The rain stopped...\n\n\nI wonder if Prince Sidon was able to\nstop "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "Ruta"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk14": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [5, 12]}}, {"text": "Even so, this is very troubling..."}, {"control": {"kind": "single_choice", "label": 2}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk16": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [5, 12]}}, {"text": "Now then..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": " I must devise a plan to find\nthe "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "ceremonial trident"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "..."}, {"control": {"kind": "single_choice", "label": 5}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk17": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [5, 16]}}, {"text": "The "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "ceremonial trident"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": " is used in a \nfestival to honor Champion Mipha..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "longer"}}, {"text": "\n\nThe Champion Festival's\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "Lightscale Trident"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "...\nWell, it's a fake.\nI planned to have that "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "ceremonial trident"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "\nexamined by Dento, "}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": "but on the way\nthere, I dropped it off the bridge.\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 4]}}, {"text": "It doesn't really matter. It's a fake,\nafter all..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": " I'll have to ask Dento to\nmake a new one.\nIf someone happens to pick it up,"}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": "\nthey can just keep it."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk18": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 12]}}, {"text": "It's you..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk19": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [5, 16]}}, {"text": "Still... I wonder..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": " Where I dropped that\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "ceremonial trident"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk20": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [4, 20]}}, {"text": "What is that you are holding?"}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": " It...it is\nmost certainly the "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "ceremonial trident"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "!\n\nOh, well. Go ahead and keep it."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk21": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 6]}}, {"text": "Well? "}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": "What do you want?"}, {"control": {"kind": "raw", "one": {"eight": {"unknown_1": [[255, 255, 0, 0], [255, 255, 0, 0]], "field_1": [5, 0, 6], "field_2": [0, 0, 0, 3]}}}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk22": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 4]}}, {"text": "The "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "ceremonial trident "}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "is a replica of the\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "Lightscale Trident"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": ". It is used in the\nChampion Festival.\nAt first glance, the "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "metal"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": " used looks the\nsame as that of the "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "Lightscale Trident"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": ".\n\nAnd that "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "ceremonial trident"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": "\nwas dropped under the bridge...\n\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 12]}}, {"text": "Well, it's a fake, so it doesn't matter.\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "longer"}}, {"text": "If someone finds it, they can keep it."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk23": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 1]}}, {"text": "Hm..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk24": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [5, 16]}}, {"text": "That "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "ceremonial trident"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": " you're holding..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": "\nIn addition to its combat use, it has the\nsame power as the "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "Lightscale Trident"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": ".\nOriginally, the "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "Lightscale Trident"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": " was\nmeant to lead the hero to a "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "trial"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "...\nAt least, according to the "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "legend"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": ".\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [11, 1]}}, {"text": "I believe the Champion Festival Song's\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "lyrics"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": " mention this...\n\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 4]}}, {"text": "If you find a child who loves songs,"}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": "\nhe or she might know it."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk25": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 4]}}, {"text": "It looks like something is shining"}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": "\naround "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "Veiled Falls"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "...\n\nDid you do something with the\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "ceremonial trident"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "?"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk26": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 16]}}, {"text": "Oh, well...\n\n\nAfter you left,"}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": " I remembered the legend.\n\n\nA gift from the sky...a scale of light...\nSplits the feet...of a Veiled Falls sight...\nYour trial awaits...it's glowing bright...\n...\n\n\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 4]}}, {"text": "At "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "Veiled Falls"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": ","}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": " there is a pedestal\njust like the one Lady Mipha's statue\nrests upon.\nThe legend indicates that you must\nthrust the "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "Lightscale Trident"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": " into the\nsame place as the statue of Lady Mipha.\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 18]}}, {"text": "We tried to do just that long ago, but\nnothing happened.\n\nPerhaps someone with the Champion's\ntalents might have better luck..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk27": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 4]}}, {"text": "How is that "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "ceremonial trident"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": " faring?\n\n\nIf the "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "ceremonial trident"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": " breaks or\nis lost,"}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": " please let Dento at the\nworkshop know."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk28": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [8, 14]}}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 125}}, {"text": "And not just any Hylian!\nYou are Link!!"}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 100}}, {"text": "\n\nOf all the Hylians Prince Sidon could\nhave brought back... What are the odds\nit would turn out to be Link?\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [2, 14]}}, {"text": "Lady Mipha's revenge..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": " I shall enact it\nhere and now!"}, {"control": {"kind": "single_choice", "label": 3}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk29": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [2, 12]}}, {"text": "You!"}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": " You were alive 100 years ago,\nso you should know all about "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "Ruta"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "!"}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "longer"}}, {"text": "\nSurely you cannot have forgotten...\nLady Mipha, our Zora Champion..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": "\nin order to help defeat Calamity Ganon,\nshe piloted the "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "Divine Beast Vah Ruta"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk30": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 4]}}, {"text": "But I do not understand... "}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "longer"}}, {"text": "Why is the\nDivine Beast sending a plague of rain\nto us and making the domain suffer?!\nI think that the rain is the tears of\nLady Mipha, who was defeated without\nfulfilling her duty!"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk31": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [2, 4]}}, {"text": "We of the Zora council have always been\nintent on stopping "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "Ruta "}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "ourselves..."}, {"control": {"kind": "raw", "one": {"eight": {"unknown_1": [], "field_1": [11, 34, 78, 112, 99, 95, 90, 111, 114, 97, 48, 50, 55, 95, 83, 112, 101, 97, 114, 4, 0, 10, 0, 6], "field_2": [0, 0, 0, 3]}}}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk32": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [2, 14]}}, {"text": "Hmph..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": " Link..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk33": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [2, 6]}}, {"text": "Well?"}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": " What could the man who stole our\nLady Mipha away "}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": "possibly have to say?"}, {"control": {"kind": "choice", "choice_labels": [11, 6], "selected_index": 0, "cancel_index": 1, "unknown": 6}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk34": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [6, 12]}}, {"text": "Now then..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "longer"}}, {"text": " What shall we do about that\nawful "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "blue"}}, {"text": "Ruta"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "..."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk35": {"attributes": "", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 80}}, {"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [6, 1]}}, {"text": "That one's a fake, anyway..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "longer"}}, {"text": " I'll just ask Dento\nto make me a new one later... "}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 100}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk36": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [5, 16]}}, {"text": "Well? What is the matter?"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk37": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [1, 11]}}, {"text": "I knew you were the same Link from 100\nyears ago..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "longer"}}, {"text": " You did a fine job this time.\n\nMay Lady Mipha's spirit live on within\nall of us...\n\n"}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk38": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 6]}}, {"text": "Say, Link..."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "longer"}}, {"text": "is that the "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "ceremonial trident"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "\nyou have there?"}, {"control": {"kind": "single_choice", "label": 5}}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk39": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [0, 6]}}, {"text": "That "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "trident"}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "..."}, {"control": {"kind": "raw", "zero": {"four": {"field_1": 0}}}}, {"text": "Hmm... "}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": "Perhaps you stand a chance."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "long"}}, {"text": "\nI advise you to listen to that "}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "red"}}, {"text": "song "}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}, {"text": "the\ndomain's children sometimes sing."}]}, "EventFlowMsg/Npc_Zora027:talk40": {"attributes": "Npc_Zora027", "contents": [{"control": {"kind": "sound", "unknown": [5, 16]}}, {"text": "Hmm... "}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": "I must prepare for the\nChampion Festival."}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": " I do not\nhave time to talk.\n"}, {"control": {"kind": "set_colour", "colour": "grey"}}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 80}}, {"text": "Where did I drop it... "}, {"control": {"kind": "pause", "length": "short"}}, {"text": "Hmmm..."}, {"control": {"kind": "text_size", "percent": 100}}, {"control": {"kind": "reset_colour"}}]}}